name: Create Lists from Comma-Delimited Strings
description:
Package contains two nodes to create lists from a text string:

1) "List of Numbers from Comma-Delimited String" - creates list of numbers from string of numbers separated by commas
Example:  inputting the string "1,1,2,3,5,8" creates the following list of six numbers: [1,1,2,3,5,8]

2) "List of Strings from Comma-Delimited String" - creates list of text strings from string of text separated by commas
Example:  inputting the string "length,width,height" creates the following list of three strings: ["length","width","height"]
contents: List of Numbers from Comma-Delimited String - Converts a string of comma-delimited numbers into a list of numbers, List of Strings from Comma-Delimited String - Create a list of strings from a single comma-delimited string
